Bobertron walked around. Pantron closley by his side. They where quite a 
team. Yes they where. But know they had to make a choice. They looked to the 
left to the maximal bases direction. They then turned to the right towards 
the destron base. They where torn between old bielefs and new recreations. 
They each sent a comm to either base. Who ever replied fort they decided 
would be their new home. The message just stated that they where two bots and 
that they where searching for a new group.(one to the cf and one to the 
magmatron's base.)
